---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="服務內容 - Hooo 好圈圈好感形象學苑">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="min-h-[70vh] flex items-center bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 via-primary-500 to-secondary-500 text-white relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/20 z-0"></div>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 sm:mb-8 leading-tight animate-fade-in">為什麼你需要一套專屬於你的
          <span class="bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-200 to-yellow-100">「形象力升級計畫」</span>？
        </h1>
        
        <div class="space-y-4 sm:space-y-6 mb-8 sm:mb-12">
          <div class="transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
            <p class="text-lg font-medium bg-white/10 p-4 rounded-lg inline-block">你有沒有想過，第一印象其實只花<span class="text-yellow-200 font-bold">0.1秒</span>就決定了？</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-left">
            <div class="bg-white/5 p-6 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-sm hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
              <p class="text-lg">不管你多有實力、工作多努力，如果形象無法傳達出你的價值，你正在默默錯失許多機會。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white/5 p-6 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-sm hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
              <p class="text-lg">形象，不只是外表，而是一種「綜合訊號」：專業度、親和力、信任感…都藏在你的一舉一動中。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-white/20 to-white/10 p-8 rounded-2xl backdrop-blur-md transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg">
          <p class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">🌟 想升職、想轉職、想創業、想做個讓人記得的人？</p>
          <p class="text-lg text-yellow-200">你需要的，是一套能升級你的「形象力系統」！</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 服務方案 Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-primary-100 text-primary-600 rounded-full font-medium mb-4">專業形象設計</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">好圈圈的三階段形象力打造方案</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">一場「由內而外」的深度探索旅程</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- 第一階段 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden group transform hover:-translate-y-1">
            <div class="h-48 bg-primary-500 relative overflow-hidden">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-400 to-primary-600 transform group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"></div>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-6xl">🌟</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8">
              <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-primary-50 text-primary-600 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4">第一階段</div>
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">美學講座｜從審美覺察開始</h4>
              <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">不只是穿搭講座，而是一場觀念的啟蒙。讓你了解「原來形象是可以設計的」，適合公司團體、社團邀請，為團隊植入品味力。</p>
              <a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 transition-colors">
                了解更多
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 第二階段 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden group transform hover:-translate-y-1">
            <div class="h-48 bg-secondary-500 relative overflow-hidden">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary-400 to-secondary-600 transform group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"></div>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-6xl">✨</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8">
              <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-secondary-50 text-secondary-600 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4">第二階段</div>
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">好感形象體驗｜實作互動一次到位</h4>
              <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">探索三大關鍵主題，讓你用3小時打通「看起來好感 vs 真正合適」的迷思，活動後還有免費諮詢 + 個人化報告，立刻知道怎麼改善自己最重要的第一印象！</p>
              <a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center text-secondary-600 hover:text-secondary-700 transition-colors">
                了解更多
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 第三階段 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden group transform hover:-translate-y-1">
            <div class="h-48 bg-primary-500 relative overflow-hidden">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-400 to-yellow-600 transform group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"></div>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-6xl">👑</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8">
              <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-yellow-50 text-yellow-600 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4">第三階段</div>
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">1對1 專屬形象IP｜打造個人品牌定位</h4>
              <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-3 mb-6">
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                  </svg>
                  個人色彩分析
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                  </svg>
                  專屬風格與香氛定位
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                  </svg>
                  彩妝教學與穿搭實作
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                  </svg>
                  專屬形象報告書
                </li>
              </ul>
              <div class="bg-yellow-50 p-4 rounded-lg mb-6">
                <p class="text-yellow-800 text-sm">還可加購陪購、短影音，直接進化成「質感系個人品牌」！</p>
              </div>
              <a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center text-yellow-600 hover:text-yellow-700 transition-colors">
                了解更多
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- ㄅㄡ -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-50 to-white rounded-3xl p-12 shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 text-gray-800">🧠 有人說：「形象這種事，不就是打扮一下就好？」</h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div class="bg-primary-50 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
              <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#AA285C] mb-4">錯。形象是戰略。</p>
              <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">在這個看臉的時代，不懂形象，就等於把競爭力拱手讓人。</p>
            </div>

            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">你願意讓孩子、讓自己在職場或生活中，一再輸在「印象分」上嗎？</p>

            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-50 to-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-primary-100">
              <p class="text-lg font-medium text-[#AA285C]">現在就開始【形象力升級計畫】，與好圈圈一起成為讓人一眼記得的你。</p>
            </div>

            <a href="#contact" class="inline-block bg-[#AA285C] text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-[#8A1F4A] transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl">
              立即開啟形象旅程
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>  
</Layout>
